title: Chicago Flag Heart Wood Ornament
description:
Inspired by the Chicago flag and a childhood spent roaming the city, the ornament is made from solid, sustainable Black Cherry wood, engraved and cut with intricate detail. Finished with a food safe oil, each piece comes with a ribbon for hanging.  Made by Nestled Pines Woodworking, a company focused on combining design, nature, and sustainability with technology to create unique works of art. Manufactured in the USA.

  • Dimensions: 3.25 x 3 x .2 in.
  • Materials: Black Cherry Woood
